    "abstract": "Recently, in IEEE Internet of Things Journal (DOI: 10.1109/JIOT.2019.2923373 ), Banerjee et al. proposed a lightweight anonymous authenticated key exchange scheme for IoT based on symmetric cryptography. In this paper, we show\nthat the proposal can not resist impersonation attacks due to vulnerable mutual authentication, and give improvements.",
